<h2 id="_4-分数与极限" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-分数与极限"><span>4. 分数与极限</span></a></h2>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><munder><mrow><mi>lim</mi><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>→</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∞</mi></mrow></munder><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi>n</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{1}{n} = 0
